</media>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-id1167793584540">
<para id="fs-id1167793584542"><emphasis effect="bold">H</emphasis></para>
</solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-id1167793584551">
<problem id="fs-id1167793584553">
<media id="fs-id1167794288058" alt="Una representación visual de un campo vectorial en dos dimensiones. Las flechas son más grandes cuanto más se alejan del origen. Se extienden hacia fuera y se alejan del origen en un patrón radial.">
<image mime-type="image/jpeg" src="../../media/CNX_Calc_Figure_16_01_214.jpg"/>
</media>
</problem>
</exercise>
<para id="fs-id1167794288083">En los siguientes ejercicios, supongamos que <m:math><m:mrow><m:mstyle mathvariant="bold" mathsize="normal"><m:mtext>F</m:mtext></m:mstyle><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mstyle mathvariant="bold" mathsize="normal"><m:mtext>i</m:mtext></m:mstyle><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mi>y</m:mi><m:mstyle mathvariant="bold" mathsize="normal"><m:mtext>j</m:mtext></m:mstyle><m:mo>,</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> <m:math><m:mrow><m:mstyle mathvariant="bold" mathsize="normal"><m:mtext>G</m:mtext></m:mstyle><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>-</m:mtext><m:mi>y</m:mi><m:mstyle mathvariant="bold" mathsize="normal"><m:mtext>i</m:mtext></m:mstyle><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mstyle mathvariant="bold" mathsize="normal"><m:mtext>j</m:mtext></m:mstyle><m:mo>,</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> y <m:math><m:mrow><m:mstyle mathvariant="bold" mathsize="normal"><m:mtext>H</m:mtext></m:mstyle><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mstyle mathvariant="bold" mathsize="normal"><m:mtext>i</m:mtext></m:mstyle><m:mo>–</m:mo><m:mi>y</m:mi><m:mstyle mathvariant="bold" mathsize="normal"><m:mtext>j</m:mtext></m:mstyle><m:mo>.</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> Empareje los campos vectoriales con sus gráficos en <m:math><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mtext>I</m:mtext><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mtext>IV</m:mtext></m:mrow><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mo>.</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math></para><list id="fs-id1167794223613" list-type="enumerated" number-style="lower-alpha">
<item><m:math><m:mrow><m:mstyle mathvariant="bold" mathsize="normal"><m:mtext>F</m:mtext></m:mstyle><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mstyle mathvariant="bold" mathsize="normal"><m:mtext>G</m:mtext></m:mstyle></m:mrow></m:math></item>
<item><m:math><m:mrow><m:mstyle mathvariant="bold" mathsize="normal"><m:mtext>F</m:mtext></m:mstyle><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mstyle mathvariant="bold" mathsize="normal"><m:mtext>H</m:mtext></m:mstyle></m:mrow></m:math></item>
<item><m:math><m:mrow><m:mstyle mathvariant="bold" mathsize="normal"><m:mtext>G</m:mtext></m:mstyle><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mstyle mathvariant="bold" mathsize="normal"><m:mtext>H</m:mtext></m:mstyle></m:mrow></m:math></item>
<item><m:math><m:mrow><m:mtext>- −</m:mtext><m:mstyle mathvariant="bold" mathsize="normal"><m:mtext>F</m:mtext></m:mstyle><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mstyle mathvariant="bold" mathsize="normal"><m:mtext>G</m:mtext></m:mstyle></m:mrow></m:math></item>
</list>
<exercise id="fs-id1167793568655">
